author: @calia.castellan
text:
Rooftop Farming (or mostly backyard gardening nowadays) is something that the majority of us had been doing in this time of the pandemic. 

It definitely made some of us appreciate further the nature of providing what we need, most especially in terms of food and medicine. Moreover, we were able to experience being responsible for a (plant) life, which entails great effort, care, and attention to do so.

Hence, I can resonate with what Taeyong has said, "Nature is powerful." Therefore, this is something that we should continuously care for as its stewards. 

Thank you for promoting its importance, Taeyong and Sungchan 💚
